R e a d m e
-----------

Set CustomData on every piston that needs to extend to drill to contain the string "extend_to_drill".

Set CustomData on every piston that needs to retract to drill to contain the string "retract_to_drill".

Set CustomData on every rotor that needs to turn when drilling to contain the string drill_rotor.

Every drill on the grid will be found and activated.

Buttons that call the script can contain the parameter "drill", "park" or "stop".

Debug Info
----------
Any screen that has custom data containing "[AutoMinerDebug]" 
will have various debugging messages printed to it.